OL,7,G0705 Couples Come Dine with Me
OL,8,     FIn London, Joy and Jerry serve up
OL,9,     Fsome mystery meat. Novices Ricky
OL,10,     Fand Becca struggle to cook their
OL,11,     FThai banquet. And firefighters
OL,12,     FSian and Tim serve the second Thai
OL,13,     Fmenu in as many days.
